          <div class="heading mt">
          Our Values
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="para">
          <ul class="list">
            <!-- <li>
    <i class="bi bi-dot"></i>
    Customers are our highest priority.
    </li> -->
            <li>
            <i class="bi bi-dot"></i>
            <span>
              <b>Customer Focus</b>: Customers are our highest priority. We are committed to exceeding their
              expectations
              and building
              long-term partnerships.
            </span>
            </li>
            <li>

            <i class="bi bi-dot"></i>
            <span>
              <b>Innovation</b>: We embrace continuous improvement and innovation to remain at the forefront of
              our
              industry.
            </span>
            </li>
            <li>
            <i class="bi bi-dot"></i>
            <span>
              <b>Integrity</b>: We conduct our business with honesty, transparency, and responsibility.
            </span>
            </li>
            <li>
            <i class="bi bi-dot"></i>
            <span>
              Excellence: We strive for excellence in every aspect of our work, from design to delivery.
            </span>
            </li>
            <li>
            <i class="bi bi-dot"></i>
            <span>
              <b>Teamwork</b>: We believe in working collaboratively, valuing each team member’s contribution,
              and
              achieving common goals.
            </span>
            </li>
            <li>
            <i class="bi bi-dot"></i>
            <span>
              <b>Growth</b>: We play to our strengths and constantly analyze new opportunities for development.
            </span>
            </li>
            <li>
            <i class="bi bi-dot"></i>
            <span>
              We play to our strength & analyze.We never lose sight of our customers.
            </span>
            </li>
          </ul>
